title: Star Wars fans braced for new trailer and advance ticket sales - Harwich and Manningtree Standard
text:
Star Wars fans around the world are to be treated to a new trailer and advance ticket sales, two months before the hotly anticipated film hits cinemas. A new trailer for Star Wars: The Force Awakens will debut during half-time at the New York Giants v Philadelphia Eagles American football game in Philadelphia on Monday evening, Lucasfilm announced.
 Harwich and Manningtree Standard.
